{"tid":1058191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓 國 瑜 '“非常可能” 會 晤 中聯辦主任","createTime":"2019-03-12T11:27:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T15:23:45.000Z","uid":62257,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"82be876d940b814fe7b30b993722db09397caa98","tid":1058191,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T11:27:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/taiwan-mayor-expected-to-meet-carrie-lam-and-chinese-officials-20190307/4817563.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Ftaiwan-mayor-expected-to-meet-carrie-lam-and-chinese-officials-20190307%2F4817563.html&d=fcvOs274DMK6OEArnk0La%2FilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=dd574235\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/taiwan-mayor-expected-to-meet-carrie-lam-and-chinese-officials-20190307/4817563.html</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣國民黨政治明星、高雄市長韓國瑜定於3月22至28日訪問港澳深廈四個城市。儘管韓國瑜強調此行主要目的是&ldquo;拼經濟&rdquo;，不過港媒近日熱議韓國瑜在香港除會晤特首林鄭月娥外，是否將會晤北京駐港最高官員中聯辦主任王志民。<br />\n近年被馬雲收購的香港英文的南華早報星期四報導，港府和親北京建制派消息表示，對北京友善的韓國瑜&ldquo;非常可能&rdquo;會晤中聯辦主任王王志民。<br />\n報導還表示，港府消息還稱，韓國瑜在22日訪港當天與特首林鄭月娥會晤時，有關香港修改引渡條例，將台灣列入以個案形式處理移交逃犯申請地區的問題，不會列入雙方討論的議程。<br />\nNow新聞台也報導，韓國瑜留港短短一天，有機會與行政長官林鄭月娥會面。消息更指不排除會與西環官員見面，包括中聯辦主任王志民會晤。如果成事，這個安排將是&ldquo;破天荒&rdquo;。<br />\n報導還表示，香港在兩岸關係上一直有特殊角色， 北京將台灣的統一定位在&ldquo;兩制&rdquo;上面，香港可能會起示範作用。不過，從台灣角度，看見香港的實踐情況也可能覺得，這未必是台灣的答案。<br />\n在中國國家主席習近平年初對台灣提出的&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;政策講話後，台灣總統蔡英文和民進黨都嚴詞拒絕，而親中國的國民黨也表示難以接受。<br />\n外界普遍認為，香港和澳門實施&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;20多年來，要求民主的團體和聲音都隨著中國強化其獨裁統治而遭到壓制，新聞和言論自由也受到威脅，台灣對香港&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;的實踐感到反感。<br />\n據高雄市政府公佈，高雄市長韓國瑜計劃3月22 日首站到訪香港，停留一天，23日轉赴澳門。"},{"pid":"8866c0d070ff320c22e3a3cdf72bb9a4d2fd8235","tid":1058191,"uid":141151,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T11:29:06.000Z","msg":"好玩唔玩，玩台灣政客香港會晤中聯辦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國仲唔搞關係法咩"},{"pid":"3ae05f2745e3c8a105665f8b5d6b9fce04183ab8","tid":1058191,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T11:30:50.000Z","msg":"述職<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://res.zohi.tv/a/10001/201903/c613b8315f0baf513d86a6cec4da0e0c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fres.zohi.tv%2Fa%2F10001%2F201903%2Fc613b8315f0baf513d86a6cec4da0e0c.JPG&h=9546d437&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b17643757439a7fe0049ff19da2327f54697bef","tid":1058191,"uid":62257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8866c0d070ff320c22e3a3cdf72bb9a4d2fd8235","tid":1058191,"uid":141151,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T11:29:06.000Z","msg":"好玩唔玩，玩台灣政客香港會晤中聯辦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國仲唔搞關係法咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T11:33:03.000Z","msg":"人哋要向中聯辦交代呀嘛"},{"pid":"57a40ca9be6bffc9a4b73de2fd263cc04f521600","tid":1058191,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T11:44:32.000Z","msg":"述職？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63747fb74cc91f4bb05a0864e1b211235fe0ae0f","tid":1058191,"uid":224066,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T11:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xbd4Xmf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXbd4Xmf.jpg&h=8dcf68fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c745d2fb7c5a11f3b15400529f69e8c2bcf65a30","tid":1058191,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T11:55:59.000Z","msg":"黃毓民：韓國瑜訪港無阻滯～ 韓風凌厲！天王靠攏！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1053879\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1053879</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8594e280920fb6f726b25d28215e37bcd523d